Notes
-----

- used last version of moderncv (0.14); system version of moderncv was replaced by new one
- when converting my photo from .png to .eps (with GIMP) used 106.37 as width and heigh
- to add some cyrillic text use:
  - %\usepackage[ukrainian,USenglish]{babel}
  - % \cvitem{Ukrainian Name}{\foreignlanguage{ukrainian}{Проценко Семен Вiкторович}}


